  <item nodeId="node-157">
    <command xml:space="preserve">examine old newspaper</command>
    <result xml:space="preserve">A newspaper from 2 weeks ago with a disturbing front page... "Corruption may win - Jo&#x00E3;o and Maria Alfonzo found dead in a dark alley". How can't I remember that day?&#x000A;&#x000A;&gt;</result>
