  <item nodeId="node-190">
    <command xml:space="preserve">go inside</command>
    <result xml:space="preserve">&gt; A strange man bumps into you.&#x000A;Hey! Watch where you're going!&#x000A;He's already gone... could have at least apologized.&#x000A;&#x000A;Judge Richards's Chamber&#x000A;I think I remember this guy... didn't I use to come here with my mother when I was a child? Maybe she was on one of his trials in the past...&#x000A;&#x000A;&gt;</result>
    <commentary xml:space="preserve"></commentary>
    <changed>NO</changed>
  </item>
  <item nodeId="node-191">
