  <item nodeId="node-363">
    <command xml:space="preserve">go inside</command>
    <result xml:space="preserve">Tiara Palace&#x000A;Of all the places i expected to find here, a damn palace is the last one. It doesn't really look like a palace, it's more like a rainbow, glittery nightclub stuck at the end of a long, narrow alleyway.&#x000A;&#x000A;It has a small little entrance sitting at the bottom of a facade that still manages to be imposing desipite its proportions.&#x000A;&#x000A;There's a bouncer dressed like a clown waiting at the door, it doesn't look like he's gonna let me in, not while looking like this i'm guessin".&#x000A;&#x000A;&gt;</result>
    <commentary xml:space="preserve"></commentary>
    <changed>NO</changed>
    <children>
      <child nodeId="node-364"/>
    </children>
  </item>
